{"id": "ChIJ2byf0Qq7woARVE90VJm4PiU", "rating": 4.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 675, "displayName": {"text": "Artelice Pâtisserie", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ2byf0Qq7woARVE90VJm4PiU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205NmIyZHVNMGxOZWxBMFNuWnJjV2hmWkY4MVUyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I came here the other day to see what all the hype was about regarding the fruit pastries everyone has been talking about in Los Angeles. I visited this local spot on Olympic Boulevard, and I was definitely impressed.\n\nThe shop was clean, welcoming, and had a great atmosphere. Unfortunately, I arrived later in the day, so it seemed like they were starting to run low on some of their inventory. Even so, I was able to pick up a few items, including three mango pastries, which I absolutely loved. I also grabbed a couple of other treats for my partner who was with me.\n\nTo top it off, they even included a few complimentary items, which was a very nice gesture and greatly appreciated. Overall, I had a great experience and was thankful for the opportunity to visit and review this location.\n\nIf you're looking for delicious fruit pastries and a friendly local business to support, I highly recommend stopping by. This is definitely a spot worth checking out.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I came here the other day to see what all the hype was about regarding the fruit pastries everyone has been talking about in Los Angeles. I visited this local spot on Olympic Boulevard, and I was definitely impressed.\n\nThe shop was clean, welcoming, and had a great atmosphere. Unfortunately, I arrived later in the day, so it seemed like they were starting to run low on some of their inventory. Even so, I was able to pick up a few items, including three mango pastries, which I absolutely loved. I also grabbed a couple of other treats for my partner who was with me.\n\nTo top it off, they even included a few complimentary items, which was a very nice gesture and greatly appreciated. Overall, I had a great experience and was thankful for the opportunity to visit and review this location.\n\nIf you're looking for delicious fruit pastries and a friendly local business to support, I highly recommend stopping by. This is definitely a spot worth checking out.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Abram C", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100059845287036481331/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2M0Dyd_gFQnEcdnsTmbv8yDPgzt9hJoV1PrF8Zs93qQIkAcIQ8g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-21T17:03:09.289610471Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205NmIyZHVNMGxOZWxBMFNuWnJjV2hmWkY4MVUyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205NmIyZHVNMGxOZWxBMFNuWnJjV2hmWkY4MVUyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb0ad19fbcd9:0x253eb89954744f54"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2byf0Qq7woARVE90VJm4PiU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pobVFuSlRZVUZzZFVrNGFDMVZSSEZtWWpKb1RIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I absolutely loved this place! I tried their Orange Blossom pastry, and the aroma instantly took me back to the springtime scents of northern Iran — something I never expected to find here. It was delicate, fragrant, and beautifully made.\n\nI’m so happy to have discovered such a unique and outstanding pastry shop. Everything feels authentic, high-quality, and crafted with so much care. This place is definitely a gem!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I absolutely loved this place! I tried their Orange Blossom pastry, and the aroma instantly took me back to the springtime scents of northern Iran — something I never expected to find here. It was delicate, fragrant, and beautifully made.\n\nI’m so happy to have discovered such a unique and outstanding pastry shop. Everything feels authentic, high-quality, and crafted with so much care. This place is definitely a gem!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Penny Amd", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101293656265553537059/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVBLXbrJXSNFceP6XTNVtA2bL4Z9iknid40BL_ezyXk6I1kQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-10T05:54:02.829024534Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pobVFuSlRZVUZzZFVrNGFDMVZSSEZtWWpKb1RIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pobVFuSlRZVUZzZFVrNGFDMVZSSEZtWWpKb1RIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb0ad19fbcd9:0x253eb89954744f54"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2byf0Qq7woARVE90VJm4PiU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSV1dYaG9jRGhCVVcwdGMwVTNTVXMyZEZWRWEyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Artelice Pâtisserie is a really unique spot and definitely worth checking out. It’s super easy to get to right off the street, and the pastries look and taste premium. At around $10 an item, the pricing is exactly what you'd expect for high-end desserts, and the flavors absolutely deliver. Everything I tried was fantastic.\n\nBut here's a massive heads-up: plan to eat your treats right there.\n\nAlmost everything they make is mousse-based, which means they do not travel well. I even bought one of their \"cold bags\" to take my pastries back to my hotel, and they were already starting to melt just 20 minutes later.\n\nI highly recommend dropping in for a treat, but save yourself the heartbreak of a melted dessert and just enjoy it in or right outside the shop!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Artelice Pâtisserie is a really unique spot and definitely worth checking out. It’s super easy to get to right off the street, and the pastries look and taste premium. At around $10 an item, the pricing is exactly what you'd expect for high-end desserts, and the flavors absolutely deliver. Everything I tried was fantastic.\n\nBut here's a massive heads-up: plan to eat your treats right there.\n\nAlmost everything they make is mousse-based, which means they do not travel well. I even bought one of their \"cold bags\" to take my pastries back to my hotel, and they were already starting to melt just 20 minutes later.\n\nI highly recommend dropping in for a treat, but save yourself the heartbreak of a melted dessert and just enjoy it in or right outside the shop!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Bill *", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106498160584371395814/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNGjGa1-2Ki_icJiLRDKNIkXs_zp6TgIz-J_aaUgOkYKIWJirT7Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-17T23:13:37.777889118Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSV1dYaG9jRGhCVVcwdGMwVTNTVXMyZEZWRWEyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSV1dYaG9jRGhCVVcwdGMwVTNTVXMyZEZWRWEyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb0ad19fbcd9:0x253eb89954744f54"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2byf0Qq7woARVE90VJm4PiU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210dWQzbE5TM0Z2TVdSbVVrNVhZelJ3VERBMWFHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place is truly unique — we need more spots like this in Los Angeles. What makes it special is that they offer famous desserts that are usually hard to find here, like the New York Roll, as well as a pastry made with real Dubai chocolate, which is also very rare in LA.\n\nI tried both of these desserts and was absolutely impressed — they were incredible. On top of that, they have a wide variety of beautiful and very appetizing sweets to choose from.\n\nI would definitely recommend this place to anyone who loves high-quality desserts.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place is truly unique — we need more spots like this in Los Angeles. What makes it special is that they offer famous desserts that are usually hard to find here, like the New York Roll, as well as a pastry made with real Dubai chocolate, which is also very rare in LA.\n\nI tried both of these desserts and was absolutely impressed — they were incredible. On top of that, they have a wide variety of beautiful and very appetizing sweets to choose from.\n\nI would definitely recommend this place to anyone who loves high-quality desserts.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Marat Shalagin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117274232149497149591/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUV_jxWcp30sQAoGMl7FLjCHAiYKY21GP7XwC32pI2zlnTyih6Z=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-05T06:00:52.939448115Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210dWQzbE5TM0Z2TVdSbVVrNVhZelJ3VERBMWFHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210dWQzbE5TM0Z2TVdSbVVrNVhZelJ3VERBMWFHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb0ad19fbcd9:0x253eb89954744f54"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ2byf0Qq7woARVE90VJm4PiU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210eFNWRk1lVlpyTjJnMU5DMWtNMjVCVFZWblJtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Beautiful desserts with tasty fillings 😋\nMango is my favorite one.\nPastry is great as well.\nI didn’t like the coffee though.. too sour for my liking.\nThe service is absolutely amazing, the workers are very friendly and helpful ❤️", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Beautiful desserts with tasty fillings 😋\nMango is my favorite one.\nPastry is great as well.\nI di